e singular set can be covered by countably many $C^2$\nmanifolds, up to a lower dimensional subset.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Dec 2018 16:34:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Feb 2019 04:22:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 2 Oct 2020 07:19:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-25"}
