s and if d > 2, then every\nelement of L(I^d) is only a join of meets of elements from the colimit of these\nembeddings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Dec 2018 15:51:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Dec 2018 07:33:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-19"}
